<p>With <code>apply</code> would be</p>

<pre class="lang-py prettyprint-override"><code>s['c'] = s.apply(lambda x: [int(x.A == i) for i in x.B], axis=1)
s
        A                  B          c
0   hello  [all, say, hello]  [0, 0, 1]
1    good   [good, for, you]  [1, 0, 0]
2      my         [so, hard]     [0, 0]
3  pandas           [pandas]        [1]
4   wrong                 []         []
</code></pre>
